Gene Expression Analysis Platform


Prerequisites - R and Python3, with the following packages:

R Packages:
  - yaml
  - tidyverse
  - BiocManager

BiocManager packages:
  - BiocParallel
  - affycoretools
  - affyPLM
  - hgu133plus2.db
  - qvalue

Python3 packages (in requirements.txt):
  - flask
  - flask-session


Instructions to set up and start the web app:

1. Setup web app in your environment
cd webapp
pip3 install --upgrade pip
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

2. Set FLASK_APP environmental variable (required)
export FLASK_APP=app

3. Run the web app (replace xxxx with a port #)
flask run -h 0.0.0.0 -p xxxx
